N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.6 - Party; Commissioner of Labor

State Regulations
(a) "Party" includes petitioner, applicant, respondent, Commissioner of Labor, intervenor, and objector. (b) "Commissioner" when referred to in these
rules means the Commissioner of Labor, and may be used interchangeably with the
terms "Department of Labor," "Department," and "DOL."
